Shameless is an American comedy-drama series adapted by John Wells based upon the British series of the same name. It premiered on Showtime on January 9, 2011. The second season premiered on January 8, 2012. On February 1, 2012, "Shameless" was renewed for a third season, which premiered January 13, 2013. On January 29, 2013, Showtime renewed "Shameless" for a fourth season.
Episodes.
Season 4 (2014).
On January 29, 2013, Showtime renewed "Shameless" for a fourth season, to premiere in 2014.
